Subject: Re: [T2] RE:Steering wheel

Loosen the center shaft nut under the horn button.

Now smack the steering wheel under the edge at 9 o'clock and 3 o'clock 
in an upward motion with open palms facing up. Usually after 3-4 smacks 
many steering wheels will pop right off. if not, time to break out the 
wheel puller.

Chris in TN
